{{Top|legends=Garbage pit}}
'''Garbage chutes''' were used to transport garbage into a [[garbage compactor]].<ref name="PLFB">{{SWKidsYouTube|series=Icons of the Force|text=Princess Leia Fights Back!|video=upkp6j7S69U}}</ref> In [[1 BBY]],<ref name="GA">''[[Star Wars: Galactic Atlas: Updated Edition]]''</ref> on a [[Rescue of Leia Organa|mission]] to rescue [[Princess]] [[Leia Skywalker Organa Solo|Leia Organa]] from the [[DS-1 Orbital Battle Station|Death Star]], [[Farmer|farmboy]] [[Luke Skywalker]], [[smuggler]] [[Han Solo]], and [[Wookiee]] [[Chewbacca]], alongside Leia,<ref name="Episode IV">{{Film|IV}}</ref> went down a garbage chute<ref name="PLFB" /> into an [[Galactic Empire|Imperial]] [[garbage masher 3263827|garbage masher]] to escape [[Stormtrooper]]s.<ref name="Episode IV">{{Film|IV}}</ref>

